課程教材 Course Material
	    Molecular Biology of the Cell (Fifth Edition), 2007, by Bruce Alberts, Alexander Johnson, Julian Lewis, Martin Raff, Keith Roberts, Peter Walter. Publisher: Garland Science
 Molecular Cloning: A Laboratory Manual (Fourth Edition), 2012, by Michael R. Green and Joseph Sambrook. Publisher: Cold Spring Harbor Laboratory Press. Biotechnology, Academic Cell Update”, 2012, by Clark, D.P. and Pazdernik, N.J.. Publisher: Academic Press    

參考書目 References
